  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RIDE A ROLLER COASTER AT HOME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Epic Roller Coasters</strong>, you'll get the same feeling of real roller coasters in places and situations that you will probably never have in real life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore adrenaline in many places: magical lands, a valley where the dinosaurs are still alive, past-time travels, haunted places, dystopian futures, wonders of architecture, fairy tales, paradisiacal places, and much more.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Three different modes of endless fun for you</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/46d9253e83e49ebf86d6c0e0b0da3b18.poster.avif?t=1768932227\" width=586 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/46d9253e83e49ebf86d6c0e0b0da3b18.webm?t=1768932227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/46d9253e83e49ebf86d6c0e0b0da3b18.mp4?t=1768932227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic: </strong>Hold on tight and feel like riding a roller coaster alone or with your family and friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/d747511f072fda67b5326f1db7dc9db5.poster.avif?t=1768932227\" width=586 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/d747511f072fda67b5326f1db7dc9db5.webm?t=1768932227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/d747511f072fda67b5326f1db7dc9db5.mp4?t=1768932227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shooter:</strong> The perfect combination of two amazing universes! Roller coasters rides and target shooting competitions! Are you a true gunslinger?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/eea25bdd36874f8f88f92aaa6ca9b170.poster.avif?t=1768932227\" width=586 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/eea25bdd36874f8f88f92aaa6ca9b170.webm?t=1768932227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/eea25bdd36874f8f88f92aaa6ca9b170.mp4?t=1768932227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Race:</strong> Take control of the cart on your own time and speed to challenge yourself and your friends to conquer the fastest roller coaster race lap!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather your friends to ride your favorite roller coasters with you. Compete to discover who’s the faster rider or collaborate in the Shooter mode to hit as many targets as you can. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Compatibility with Motion Simulators</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/9c3e1a587292c384a26ea597e5ee7339.poster.avif?t=1768932227\" width=586 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/9c3e1a587292c384a26ea597e5ee7339.webm?t=1768932227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/9c3e1a587292c384a26ea597e5ee7339.mp4?t=1768932227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level up </strong>your Epic Roller Coaster rides with motion and haptics simulators. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapons, companions and carts</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t ride alone. Choose one of our virtual companions to ride beside you, giving you a real amusement park feel. But if you are shooting or racing, check out the carts and weapons that match with more intense and fun. </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RIDE A ROLLER COASTER AT HOME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Epic Roller Coasters</strong>, you'll get the same feeling of real roller coasters in places and situations that you will probably never have in real life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore adrenaline in many places: magical lands, a valley where the dinosaurs are still alive, past-time travels, haunted places, dystopian futures, wonders of architecture, fairy tales, paradisiacal places, and much more.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Three different modes of endless fun for you</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/46d9253e83e49ebf86d6c0e0b0da3b18.poster.avif?t=1768932227\" width=586 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/46d9253e83e49ebf86d6c0e0b0da3b18.webm?t=1768932227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/46d9253e83e49ebf86d6c0e0b0da3b18.mp4?t=1768932227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic: </strong>Hold on tight and feel like riding a roller coaster alone or with your family and friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/d747511f072fda67b5326f1db7dc9db5.poster.avif?t=1768932227\" width=586 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/d747511f072fda67b5326f1db7dc9db5.webm?t=1768932227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/d747511f072fda67b5326f1db7dc9db5.mp4?t=1768932227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shooter:</strong> The perfect combination of two amazing universes! Roller coasters rides and target shooting competitions! Are you a true gunslinger?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/eea25bdd36874f8f88f92aaa6ca9b170.poster.avif?t=1768932227\" width=586 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/eea25bdd36874f8f88f92aaa6ca9b170.webm?t=1768932227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/eea25bdd36874f8f88f92aaa6ca9b170.mp4?t=1768932227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Race:</strong> Take control of the cart on your own time and speed to challenge yourself and your friends to conquer the fastest roller coaster race lap!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather your friends to ride your favorite roller coasters with you. Compete to discover who’s the faster rider or collaborate in the Shooter mode to hit as many targets as you can. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Compatibility with Motion Simulators</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/9c3e1a587292c384a26ea597e5ee7339.poster.avif?t=1768932227\" width=586 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/9c3e1a587292c384a26ea597e5ee7339.webm?t=1768932227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/787790/extras/9c3e1a587292c384a26ea597e5ee7339.mp4?t=1768932227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Level up </strong>your Epic Roller Coaster rides with motion and haptics simulators. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapons, companions and carts</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don’t ride alone. Choose one of our virtual companions to ride beside you, giving you a real amusement park feel. But if you are shooting or racing, check out the carts and weapons that match with more intense and fun. </p>",
